<div id="sectionRoommates" class="hidden">
    <div data-c-grid="gutter(all, 1)">
        <div data-c-grid-item="base(1of1)">
            <span id="roommates"></span>
            <h2 data-gc-section-status="incomplete" data-c-margin="top(3) bottom(1)" data-c-heading="h2" data-c-padding="bottom(1)">
                <i class="material-icons">error</i>
                <i class="material-icons">warning</i>
                <i class="material-icons">check_circle</i>
                Roommates and Cohabitants
            </h2>
            <p data-c-margin="bottom(normal)">Please complete this section if you have a roommate or cohabitant who is:</p>
            <ul data-c-margin="bottom(normal)">
                <li>over 18 years of age</li>
                <li>currently living at the same address as you in a non-conjugal relationship, including relatives and non-relatives</li>
                <li>not a former spouse or common-law partner listed</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Ensure that you provide the legal names of all roommates and cohabitants. If you are a student living in residence, list only the person(s) with whom you share a dorm room or apartment.</p>
        </div>
        {# Cohabitation Confirmation #}
        <div data-c-input="radio" data-c-grid-item="base(1of1)">
            <label for="cohabitantConfirmation">Do you have any roommates or cohabitants to declare that meet the requirements outlined above?</label>
            <span>Required</span>
            <div id="cohabitantConfirmation" role="radiogroup">
                <label for="cohabitantConfirmationYes" data-gc-cohabitants-true-trigger>
                    <input id="cohabitantConfirmationYes" required name="cohabitantConfirmation" type="radio" />
                    <span>Yes</span>
                </label>
                <label for="cohabitantConfirmationNo" data-gc-cohabitants-false-trigger>
                    <input id="cohabitantConfirmationNo" required name="cohabitantConfirmation" type="radio" />
                    <span>No</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <span>This input has an error.</span>
        </div>
        {# Roommates / Cohabitants #}
        <div data-c-grid-item="base(1of1)" data-gc-cohabitants-true class="hidden">
            <p data-c-margin="bottom(normal)">Please provide details for each roommate/cohabitant below. You can add a roommate/cohabitant by clicking the button and completing the form.</p>
            <div data-gc-residence data-c-margin="bottom(double)">
                <div data-gc-residence-null data-c-border="all(thin, solid, gray)" data-c-background="gray(10)" data-c-radius="rounded" data-c-padding="normal" data-c-align="base(center)">
                    <p>You haven't added any information yet.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div data-c-align="base(right)">
                <button data-c-button="solid(c1)" data-c-radius="rounded" data-c-dialog-id="cohabitant-dialog" data-c-dialog-action="open" type="button">
                    Add a Roommate/Cohabitant
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>